videos.description: Grayson Allen dishes to Luke Kennard for a 3-point shot as part of Duke's early 9-0 run against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen sets up Luke Kennard 3

videos.description: Grayson Allen takes the ball the length of the court and connects with Luke Kennard for another 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Allen finds Kennard again for 3-pointer

videos.description: 1H (12:32) DUKE Luke Kennard made Two Point Tip Shot.
videos.headline: Luke Kennard stays hot with the tip in layup

videos.description: Grayson Allen does a nice job of keeping the ball in play and takes it to the hoop for a first-half bucket, his first field goal of the night.
videos.headline: Allen puts up an easy bucket

videos.description: Grayson Allen drains a 3-pointer and draws a foul to effort a 4-point play in the first half.
videos.headline: Allen skillfully completes 4-point play
Frank Jackson drives for the and-1 layup

videos.description: 1H (1:14) DUKE Luke Kennard made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Grayson Allen.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen finds Luke Kennard for his fourth 3 of the half

videos.description: Jayson Tatum sets up Harry Giles for a sweet second-half alley-oop to extend Duke's lead over Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Giles hammers home an alley-oop for Duke
Marques Bolden grabs the rebound and slams down the two handed flush

videos.description: 2H (10:57) DUKE Jayson Tatum made Dunk. Assisted by Matt Jones.
videos.headline: J. Tatum cuts to the basket for a powerful dunk
Jayson Tatum makes the layup with the foul off good ball movement

videos.description: Duke's Harry Giles finishes a tough alley-oop from Matt Jones in the second half, giving Giles his first-career double-double.
videos.headline: Giles earns first double-double with sweet alley-oop

videos.description: Postgame breakdown of Duke's 53 point victory over Georgia Tech
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown of Duke's 53 point victory over Georgia Tech

videos.description: Jay Williams reacts to Grayson Allen's suspension lasting one game and voices his opinion that the ACC should have handled Allen's suspension instead of Mike Krzyzewski.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Williams: ACC should have handled Allen suspension) 2017/1/4 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Williams: ACC should have handled Allen suspension

videos.description: Mike Krzyzewski feels comfortable with the punishment handed down to Grayson Allen.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Coach K on Allen: 'Appropriate what we've done') 2017/1/4 SC

videos.headline: Coach K on Allen: 'Appropriate what we've done'

videos.description: Grayson Allen takes responsibility for his actions in tripping opponents and reveals that coach Mike Krzyzewski was the one who approved Allen's return after one game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Grayson Allen eager to move on from tripping incidents) 2017/01/04

videos.headline: Grayson Allen eager to move on from tripping incidents

videos.description: Coach K sits down with Jay Bilas and dives into the decision to bring Grayson Allen back after a one-game suspension, how the punishment was handled and Allen's new role with the team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Coach K On Allen) 2017/1/4 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Coach K on Allen: Don't need to teach in public
